1
00:02:19,239 --> 00:02:20,667
In your words,

2
00:02:20,691 --> 00:02:22,691
you are a scumbag

3
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:24,531
Who's there?

4
00:02:27,334 --> 00:02:28,548
When did <i>We</i> allow you

5
00:02:28,572 --> 00:02:30,116
Stop preteding Hong Dou

6
00:02:32,793 --> 00:02:34,481
<i>We</i> don't know what are you talking about

7
00:02:37,197 --> 00:02:37,891
Then,

8
00:02:38,452 --> 00:02:39,452
what's this?

9
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:44,390
<i>We</i> just think it's novel

10
00:02:45,266 --> 00:02:46,479
Novel?

11
00:02:49,617 --> 00:02:51,931
Weren't you jealous at the palace?

12
00:02:55,055 --> 00:02:56,042
No

13
00:02:56,957 --> 00:02:58,478
You were jealous

14
00:02:59,659 --> 00:03:00,487
You were jealous

15
00:03:00,517 --> 00:03:01,274
You are Hong Dou

16
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,355
You are Hong Dou I knew

17
00:03:03,123 --> 00:03:04,117
Why won't you admit it?

18
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,183
Someone!

19
00:03:11,979 --> 00:03:12,879
Send him back to the Cold Palace

20
00:03:12,903 --> 00:03:14,903
Hong Dou it's me!

21
00:03:15,014 --> 00:03:15,902
- Hong Dou
- Send him back to the Cold Palace

22
00:03:29,963 --> 00:03:30,753
What are you pretending for?

23
00:03:31,133 --> 00:03:33,043
I know Xue Wuming and you even you turn into ash

24
00:03:33,343 --> 00:03:34,843
Stop right there!

25
00:03:38,343 --> 00:03:39,712
When did you sneak out?

26
00:03:43,753 --> 00:03:45,793
Are you Eunuch Duoduo or Eunuch Shaoshao?

27
00:03:46,293 --> 00:03:47,463
You also get the same hairstyle as me

28
00:03:49,543 --> 00:03:50,632
The moonlight is nice tonight

29
00:03:50,713 --> 00:03:52,593
It reminds me of my mom. Really?

30
00:03:52,593 --> 00:03:53,422
I miss my mom

31
00:03:53,633 --> 00:03:55,083
Your mother, find your mother this way

32
00:03:56,543 --> 00:03:57,463
Goodbye, goodbye

33
00:03:57,463 --> 00:03:58,173
Greetings to your mother

34
00:03:58,173 --> 00:03:59,043
Okay, no problem

35
00:03:59,343 --> 00:04:00,253
Your mother

36
00:04:02,633 --> 00:04:06,093
Jealous. Doll. Xue Wuming

37
00:04:06,883 --> 00:04:08,043
That's them

38
00:04:09,343 --> 00:04:11,043
Why don't they recognize me?

39
00:04:12,383 --> 00:04:14,593
Do you want me to chase you again?

40
00:04:25,343 --> 00:04:27,132
Your Majesty, the Princess of the Northern Kingdom has arrived

41
00:04:28,093 --> 00:04:28,632
Let her in

42
00:04:29,003 --> 00:04:29,463
Yes

43
00:04:37,843 --> 00:04:39,043
Greetings to Your Majesty

44
00:04:39,593 --> 00:04:41,632
Did you have a good rest last night, Princess?

45
00:04:41,963 --> 00:04:44,043
Thanks to Your Majesty's treat, I slept pretty well

46
00:04:46,133 --> 00:04:48,923
As the saying goes, no one shows up without a good reason

47
00:04:49,793 --> 00:04:52,253
Princess and the Prince came from afar

48
00:04:53,963 --> 00:04:56,133
Please be straightforward. What exactly brings

49
00:04:56,633 --> 00:04:57,843
you to the Southern Kingdom?

50
00:04:58,043 --> 00:04:59,423
Your Majesty is wise

51
00:05:00,003 --> 00:05:02,673
Our Northern Kingdom has always been on good terms with the Southern Kingdom

52
00:05:02,963 --> 00:05:05,923
To further strengthen the relationship between the two countries,

53
00:05:06,253 --> 00:05:07,963
we'd like to propose a marriage alliance with your country

54
00:05:09,083 --> 00:05:11,093
Has the princess taken a liking to one of my royal brothers?

55
00:05:11,293 --> 00:05:11,753
No

56
00:05:12,633 --> 00:05:15,003
Your Majesty, are you willing to marry my third brother?

57
00:05:15,043 --> 00:05:15,793
Bold!

58
00:05:15,923 --> 00:05:17,043
Her Majesty is the Empress

59
00:05:17,843 --> 00:05:19,672
Fei, don't be rude

60
00:05:20,383 --> 00:05:22,083
My third brother is simple

61
00:05:22,133 --> 00:05:23,213
and kind by nature

62
00:05:23,343 --> 00:05:24,793
He doesn't like to fight with others

63
00:05:25,133 --> 00:05:27,003
He will follow Your Majesty's wishes in everything

64
00:05:27,753 --> 00:05:29,673
If Your Majesty were with him,

65
00:05:30,043 --> 00:05:31,213
a strong woman and a gentle man

66
00:05:31,633 --> 00:05:33,293
must be a perfect match

67
00:05:35,543 --> 00:05:36,253
Then, should <i>We</i>

68
00:05:37,343 --> 00:05:39,043
respect you as

69
00:05:39,423 --> 00:05:40,213
my Imperial Sister?

70
00:05:41,133 --> 00:05:42,383
In terms of seniority...

71
00:05:42,383 --> 00:05:44,003
How dare you!

72
00:05:50,083 --> 00:05:50,963
Fei said,

73
00:05:51,753 --> 00:05:53,593
the Princess of the Northern Kingdom actually

74
00:05:53,593 --> 00:05:54,632
ask Your Majesty to fulfill the marriage alliance

75
00:05:54,923 --> 00:05:56,843
She just wants to use the power of the Southern Kingdom

76
00:05:57,463 --> 00:05:59,423
to help her brother to seize the throne in the Northern Kingdom

77
00:06:01,173 --> 00:06:02,543
It's better for her to say it directly

78
00:06:05,503 --> 00:06:07,133
Their ambition is really big

79
00:06:11,043 --> 00:06:11,843
Good,

80
00:06:12,843 --> 00:06:14,882
you need someone to help you even with stepping down

81
00:06:15,923 --> 00:06:16,423
Your Majesty

82
00:06:17,423 --> 00:06:18,083
Actually

83
00:06:20,673 --> 00:06:21,633
What do you want to say?

84
00:06:25,963 --> 00:06:27,173
What needs to be so close?

85
00:06:28,213 --> 00:06:29,593
Mr. Ye has been around for so long

86
00:06:30,343 --> 00:06:31,593
Why haven't you recognized him?

87
00:06:33,133 --> 00:06:33,713
Wuming

88
00:06:35,633 --> 00:06:36,963
Do you believe in fate?

89
00:06:37,923 --> 00:06:39,093
I never believe it

90
00:06:40,173 --> 00:06:41,633
But what happened last time

91
00:06:43,133 --> 00:06:44,253
makes me believe it

92
00:06:45,963 --> 00:06:47,423
It's the same for <i>Us</i>

93
00:06:49,793 --> 00:06:50,503
Then, Your Majesty

94
00:06:53,213 --> 00:06:54,593
As long as the people live well,

95
00:06:55,843 --> 00:06:57,043
the country is stable

96
00:06:58,293 --> 00:06:59,043
and he

97
00:07:01,133 --> 00:07:02,293
is alive, that's enough

98
00:07:12,343 --> 00:07:14,962
With the Princess of the Northern Kingdom arriving here,

99
00:07:15,503 --> 00:07:17,293
I'm much humbled

100
00:07:18,343 --> 00:07:21,093
I have long heard that the Second Prince of the Southern Kingdom

101
00:07:21,093 --> 00:07:22,422
is a man of great talent and ambitions,

102
00:07:23,003 --> 00:07:25,173
and is the most capable of all the princes

103
00:07:25,633 --> 00:07:27,543
But I've always been curious about one thing

104
00:07:27,843 --> 00:07:28,753
Curious about what?

105
00:07:28,963 --> 00:07:30,423
I'll just be straightforward

106
00:07:30,753 --> 00:07:33,083
Being under the Crown Prince then

107
00:07:33,083 --> 00:07:34,293
was understandable

108
00:07:34,543 --> 00:07:36,043
Maybe it was the Late Emperor's preference

109
00:07:36,383 --> 00:07:37,213
But now,

110
00:07:37,213 --> 00:07:39,343
you are inferior to a woman

111
00:07:47,633 --> 00:07:49,923
It is said that the royal family of the Northern Kingdom is very complex

112
00:07:50,673 --> 00:07:52,843
It's true. The survived ones

113
00:07:53,213 --> 00:07:54,383
are not ordinary people

114
00:07:54,793 --> 00:07:56,343
No need to beat around the bush

115
00:07:56,663 --> 00:07:58,084
We can talk about cooperation

116
00:07:58,471 --> 00:08:00,313
I never cooperate with women

117
00:08:01,328 --> 00:08:03,049
Even for the throne?

118
00:08:04,277 --> 00:08:05,337
Princess

119
00:08:05,973 --> 00:08:07,107
wants me to rebel?

120
00:08:07,288 --> 00:08:09,682
It is to set things right

121
00:08:10,303 --> 00:08:11,218
Why should I?

122
00:08:11,242 --> 00:08:14,534
Because we have the power
to elevate you to the throne

123
00:08:15,976 --> 00:08:16,896
Interesting

124
00:08:17,470 --> 00:08:18,124
Your conditions?

125
00:08:18,992 --> 00:08:20,038
The Empress of the Southern Kingdom

126
00:08:20,063 --> 00:08:21,921
is too disrespectful to our Northern Kingdom

127
00:08:22,889 --> 00:08:24,938
I want you to take her down
